des:
Use the Ethanol Stations alexa skill to find Ethanol Fueling stations in your zip code around the U.S. Simply enable the skill and say "Alexa, open Ethanol Stations" to begin. 

Or say "Alexa, ask Ethanol Stations..."
• get me zip code 92704 
• Is there Fueling station around 92704

This is a beta version which only holds information on basic Ethanol Fueling Station for now. Stay tuned, more features will be added soon!
